TF8&amp;qid=&amp;sr=" target="_blank"><i style="font-weight: bold;">'How to Make Great Radio'.</i>&nbsp;</a><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;">Techniques for today's presenters and&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></b></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; producers.&nbsp; Great for newcomers - and food for thought if you've been doing it&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b></span></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; years.</b></span></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;"><i><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><b><br /></b></span></i></span><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;"><i><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><b><br /></b></span></i></span><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;"><i><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><b><br /></b></span></i></span><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;"><i><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><b><br /></b></span></i></span></div><div style="background: white; border-bottom: dotted #999999 1.0pt; border-left: none; border-right: none; border-top: dotted #999999 1.0pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: dotted #999999 .75pt; mso-border-top-alt: dotted #999999 .75pt; mso-element: para-border-di